{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SAR Unicast Retransmissions Without Progress Count state"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is a 4-bit value that controls the maximum number of transmissions of segments"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of segmented messages to a Unicast destination without progress"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(i.e., without newly marking any segment as acknowledged)."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/SarTransmitterSet\/sarUnicastRetransmissionsWithoutProgressCount","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sarUnicastRetransmissionsWithoutProgressCount"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","text":"UInt8"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The maximum number of transmissions of a segment without progress is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calculated using the formula:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["SAR Unicast Retransmissions Without Progress Count + 1"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For example, "},{"code":"0b0000","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a single transmission, and "},{"code":"0b0111","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"represents 8 transmissions."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SAR Unicast Retransmissions Without Progress"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Count state"}]